179
00:15:41,221 --> 00:15:43,076
Bueno, siempre estás trabajando.

180
00:15:43,141 --> 00:15:45,410
Me da curiosidad lo que consume
todo tu tiempo.

181
00:16:32,263 --> 00:16:34,368
Guillotina.

182
00:16:37,063 --> 00:16:38,950
Eres como un funerario...

183
00:16:39,943 --> 00:16:41,831
o un sacerdote...

184
00:16:42,823 --> 00:16:46,085
o un taxidermista...
todos ellos.

185
00:16:48,456 --> 00:16:51,173
Es decir,

186
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:53,957
puedes ver vida sobre vida.

187
00:16:54,024 --> 00:16:56,446
